Attached code performs multiclass classifcation with three randomly selected segments on Bible.txt dataset. 
The idea here is to compare 14 classifiers on documents as binary, count, or tfidf vector.

Dataset: Bible.txt
Library: Sklearn
Classifiers:
  BernoulliNB
  MultinomialNB
  KNeighborsClassifier
  NearestCentroid
  LogisticRegression
  LinearSVC
  SVC
  DecisionTreeClassifier
  ExtraTreeClassifier
  ExtraTreesClassifier
  AdaBoostClassifier
  RandomForestClassifier
  Perceptron
  MLPClassifier
